data.description: Welcome to Foxwood of Chanhassen! A Gonyea community near Lake Riley conveniently right off 212 and Co Rd 101. This 2021 Stonegate built home is better than new with 70k in seller upgrades including 50k in professional landscaping, window treatments and gutters. Enjoy an open and bright main floor great room space with floor to ceiling windows, fireplace, white oak hardwoods, enameled kitchen with large center island, quartz countertops, walk-in pantry with coffee bar area, a main floor office and well thought out mudroom space. Upstairs are 4br’s and a laundry center. The spacious primary suite features a box vault ceiling and large walk-in closet. Br’s 2 and 3 are a Jack n Jill, Br 4 w private ensuite bath. Finished walkout lower level with 5th bedroom, bar area, game room and family room with fireplace overlooking the professional landscaped and fully fenced backyard. ONLY avail due to a job transfer. QUICK close available.
